{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/sass/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bwake blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3fb5e10e-ce1b-5bcf-8693-98017bd62cd9","excerpt":"It’s a CSS preprocessor/extension\nAllows us to use features that don’t exist yet in CSS\ncompiled to regular CSS form (.scss/sass) Variables in CSS mixins and…","html":"<p>It’s a CSS preprocessor/extension\nAllows us to use features that don’t exist yet in CSS\ncompiled to regular CSS form (.scss/sass)</p>\n<h2>Variables in CSS</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">$<span class=\"token property\">primary</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"blue\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>mixins and functions</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@mixin</span> transform  <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>$property<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.box</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    @include <span class=\"token function\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">rotate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>30deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Inheritance</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">%message-shared</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #ccc<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>inherit</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.message</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@extend</span> % message-shared<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.success</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@extend</span> % message-shared<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Operators</h2>\n<p>*, /, -, +</p>\n<h2>Conditionals</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@if</span> $direction === up</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@else</span> if $direction === right</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@else</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@error</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Loops</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">each in</code></pre></div>\n<h2>imports</h2>\n<p>Allows imports from other files</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"learn sass","date":"June 12, 2020","description":"Syntactically Awesome Stylesheet"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/nodejs/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"learn nodejS"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/pwa/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"progressive web apps(PWA)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3fb5e10e-ce1b-5bcf-8693-98017bd62cd9","previousPostId":"8a36650d-74d5-5fca-ba00-66f707b35751","nextPostId":"7e793ac6-f1de-55f9-a14f-55590acddbfe"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}